text: This is a list of the timelines for the history of northern New France beginning with the first exploration of North America by France through being part of the French colonial empire. *Beginnings to 1533 - northern region (present day Canada) *1534 to 1607 - northern region (Canada) *1608 to 1662 - (Quebec region) *1663 to 1759 - (Quebec region) ==See also== *Acadia (New France) - northern region colony *Canada (New France) - northern region colony *Louisiana (New France) - southern region colony *French colonization of the Americas *French Colonial Empire New France -
title: Timeline of New France history
